originalText.text: Using the right of speech guaranteed by the United States of America, I must express my opinion, if deplorable, about Dr. Cesar Alfonso, because I cannot tolerate how he have destroyed two people's life and put them down in the misery.  I have witnessed during the past 11 years, how slowly Rodolfo Valentin the famous hairstylist in New York City,  have lost his life and his businesses. He has finally lost his 2 hair salons,  and now he is also losing his apartment and not place where to live thanks to Dr. Cesar Alfonso. Rodolfo Valentin got into the infamous midlife crisis around 2007 and wanted to be emotionally involved with the most people he could. Doctor Alfonso have supported it, because he feels the same than him. Doctor Alfonso destroyed Rodolfo's 30 years relationship with his partner, who have worked elbow to elbow with Rodolfo all those years, to build the beautiful empire they had. Dr.Alfonso did not stop working in Rodolfo diseased mind, until make sure Rodolfo stay all by himself. Doctor Alfonso triumph was destroy that beautiful couple, an example of what a great relationship should be. Rodolfo got lost in life and submerged in the depravation that in the eyes of Dr. Alfonso, it was perfectly normal ! God make justice !
